com.iritech.mqel704

Class ImageKind

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iritech.mqel704.ImageKind

  • public class ImageKind
extends java.lang.Object
    Enumerates iris image kinds supported by the library. Please refer documents for ISO/IEC 19794-6 First Edition 2005-06-01 and ISO/IEC 19794-6 Second Edition 2011 to have more detailed explanation of each image kind. For IriTechâ€™s iris library, IDDK_IKIND_K1 and IDDK_IKIND_K2 are literally the same.
